Package io.micronaut.data.mongodb.annotation

Annotation Interface MongoAggregateQuery

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) @Documented @Inherited public @interface MongoAggregateQuery
Defines a custom MongoDB query for aggregating results.

3.3.0
